      "name": "SF_28 — Dual Safety Guards with Monitored Outputs (Cat.4)",
      "description": "Two dual-channel guard switches (B1, B2) monitored by a Safety Module K1 and PLC K3. Redundant output contactors Q1 and Q2 with feedback via K2 and cross-monitoring loops. Achieves Category 4 with redundancy and feedback at all stages.",
